   İş Kültürü
   In transformer businees, there is a lack of innovation and motivation
   PT Electrical Design Engineer (Güncel Çalışan) –  İstanbul, T34 – 9
   Mart 2015
   Schneider Electric is a good company to work for if you are not in
   transformer department. Mid-level managers do not have enough
   managerial capabilities and innovation is seen something to be avoided
   on the contrary to other departments.
